1. Five IT Job Roles and Their Work
IT Job Role	What the Role Does
Software Developer	            Designs and builds software applications and features.
Tester (QA Engineer)	            Checks software for bugs and ensures quality before release.
Data Analyst	            Analyzes data to find trends and support business decisions.
System Administrator	            Maintains servers, networks, and computer systems.
UI/UX Designer	            Creates user-friendly and visually appealing interfaces.


